      "description": "## What's Changed\r\n- Added manuscript as option to 'default passage format' dropdown in settings\r\n- Added additional abbreviations to referencing - [full list](https://github.com/camelChief/local-bible-ref/blob/master/src/i18n/en/books.ts)\r\n- Added customization options for quote and callout passage formats in settings\r\n- **Added support for _Bible Linker_ style vault Bible** (select _Bible Linker_ from the Bible format dropdown in settings)\r\n- **Added support for German** (including supporting German names and aliases for books of the Bible) 🎉\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\nShout out to [Hermann](https://github.com/Hermann-85) for his help in translating between English and German!\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/camelChief/local-bible-ref/compare/1.1.8...1.2.0",
